query_stock

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_stock -  This method returns alkl the stock in the shop of various types.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
object * query_stock(string type)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type of stock to return
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the array of objects of the type
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/general_shop.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns alkl the stock in the shop of various
types.  The types are:

.EP
.SO 6 2 -10

	*	jewelery 
	*	armoury 
	*	clothes 
	*	magic 
	*	none set (ie: 0, general type) 
.EO
.SP 5 5

.EP

